        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Discover comfort and style in this beautifully updated rental home in the heart of Charleston. Step into a bright, welcoming living room featuring rich wood floors and a large picture window that fills the space with natural light. The open-concept layout flows seamlessly into the dining area, perfect for hosting friends or enjoying quiet evenings at home. A flexible bonus room just off the living area offers sliding door access to the backyard ideal for a home office, playroom, or extra lounge space. The kitchen is equipped with sleek stainless steel appliances and has direct access to the backyard, perfect for enjoying meals outdoors. The home features 3 spacious bedrooms, each with wood flooring and ample closet space, providing a peaceful retreat for rest and relaxation. The updated bathroom includes a tub/shower combo designed with comfort and convenience in mind. Additional features include a dedicated laundry room and a fully fenced, landscaped backyard with a stone patio perfect for relaxing, entertaining, or letting pets play safely. This home offers the perfect blend of indoor comfort and outdoor living. Available for lease now schedule your tour today! Please text me your number so I can send the details.",
